A LOT of monk gear was up for sale tonight, probably due to the monk changes going into the patch.<br>
Also many people that I talked to are expecting that new PoP gear will cause an influx of cheaper older gear to the market.  With that in mind, I have decided to wait on the haste purchase another week or so.<br>
